data.description: This home has all the goods.  It offers an open split floor plan, Pella doors (front and back sliding doors), a large kitchen with an island, stainless farm sink and appliances, custom lighting, large dining room and barn doors on the office/play room/media room. In the roomy master bedroom there's a walk-in closet, master bath, vanity and a large soaker tub.  The large back yard is great for entertaining with a covered patio and fully vinyl fenced. Automatic sprinklers and curbed flower bed makes lawn care a breeze.  It's conveniently located close to schools, the heart of Buhl and recreation.
